headline: Despite Economic Uncertainty, US Employers Maintain Elevated Compensation Budgets for 2025, According to Mercer
summary: NEW YORK, December 10, 2024--Today, Mercer, a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC) and a global leader in helping clients realize their investment objectives, shape the future of work and enhance health and retirement outcomes for their people, released the results of the November 2024 Mercer QuickPulse™ US Compensation Planning Survey.
